	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratiam et pacem a domino etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cum nuper per publicum illum tabellarium<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1"><persName ref="person346">Ulrich Appenzeller</persName> (vgl. unten Z. 6f mit Anm. 5).</note> literas<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Oben <ref target="file11303">Nr. 1260</ref>.</note> ad te scripsissem, patrone humanissime, scriptasque obsignassem et ille discessum<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a"><hi>in der Vorlage</hi> discessu.</note> iam adornaret, rogabat d. <persName ref="person154">Miconii</persName> uxor<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Margret.</note>, ut per hunc nuntium te iuberem ipsius gratia de pecunia mea dimidiatum florenum dare <persName ref="person84">Rodolpho</persName> <persName ref="person1017">Grob</persName><note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Weiter nicht bekannt.</note> aurigae, nam eius cognatus est; hunc ego deinde ratione subducam.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hoc si, ut <persName ref="person346">Appenzellero</persName><note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5"><persName ref="person346">Ulrich Appenzeller</persName> war als amtlicher Bote nach <placeName ref="place97">Basel</placeName> geschickt worden, vgl. Zürich StA, F III 32, Seckelamtsrechnung 1538[-39], Ausgaben, S. 78.</note> mandavi, curavisti, bene est; quod si certiores a me expectavisti literas, rogo, ut nunc expedias.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="person867">Adamum</persName> Fry<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6"><persName ref="person867">Adam Frey</persName>.</note> ipse conveni, qui satis dignas gratias se nunquam pro libro<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7">Bullingers "Bericht der Kranken", vgl. oben <ref target="file11297">Nr. 1254</ref>, 12-16; 1260, 7-9.</note> referre posse ait.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pietatem certe exercet egregiam patientiaque utitur incredibili.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Deus faxit, ut hoc morbo liberetur.<pb type="edition" next="126"/></s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Te rursum rogo, charissime praeceptor, ut de pecuniis, quas habes, mihi florenum mittas, ut aestivas vestes et alia comparare possim; incredibile enim, quam me Argentina exhauserit.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De proximis enim nummis mihi missis florenos sex et sex bazones <persName ref="person9">Bedroto</persName> mittere oportuit; huic enim debui pro victu florenos novem Argentinensis monetae, ante dederam quinque.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pręterea florenum ibi insumpsi in ligno, florenum <persName ref="person1151">Herlino</persName><note xml:id="fn8" type="footnote" n="8"><persName ref="person1151">Christian Herlin</persName>.</note> pro Ptolemęi lectione dedi, dimidiatum florenum pro hypocausto cubiculoque; reliquos duos pro aliquot libellis et viatico insumpsi.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Und hatt mich fürwar also <placeName ref="place1049">Straßburg</placeName> wit hindersich<note xml:id="fn9" type="footnote" n="9">in den Rückstand.</note> bracht.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quare, patrone humanissime, te rogo, ut, si quo pacto fieri potest, aliquod saltem meo stipendio addatur augmentum, quo facilius literis operam dare possim.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Testor certe illos, quibuscum habito, me nullos inutiles sumptus impendere; sed quo modo huc penurię iam pervenerim, satis intellexisti.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Plura, quae scribam, non habeo.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Te rogo, ut hęc aequi bonique consulas meque tibi habeas commendatissimum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutat<note xml:id="fnb" type="footnote" n="b"><hi>vor</hi> Salutat <hi>gestrichenes</hi> Basile.</note> te plurimum Ioannes Reyfenstein<note xml:id="fn10" type="footnote" n="10"><persName ref="person1910">Johann Wilhelm Reiffenstein</persName>.</note> mei amantissimus et <persName ref="person238">Otho</persName><note xml:id="fn11" type="footnote" n="11"><persName ref="person238">Otto Werdmüller</persName>.</note> noster.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutabis et meis verbis uxorem<note xml:id="fn12" type="footnote" n="12">Anna, geb. Adlischwyler.</note> matremque<note xml:id="fn13" type="footnote" n="13">Anna, geb. Wiederkehr.</note> tuam, honestissimas foeminas, cum omni liberorum coetu<note xml:id="fn14" type="footnote" n="14">Vgl. oben <ref target="file11260">Nr. 1217</ref>, Anm. 46.</note>.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale bene, patrone observande.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="place97">Basileę</placeName>, ex aedibus d. <persName ref="person154">Miconii</persName>, 3. maii 1539.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tui observantissimus</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rodolphus <persName ref="person84">Gvaltherus</persName><note xml:id="fnc" type="footnote" n="c"><hi>Darunter Notiz von Bullingers Hand:</hi> Vigilius, Tubingae, Tridentinus episcopus, Urspurgensis Latinus <hi>(zur Sache vgl. unten <ref target="file11313">Nr. 1270</ref>, 7-12).</hi></note>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vere docto et pio viro M. Heinrycho Bullingero, patrono suo imprimis colendo.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="de" type="auto">An M. Heinrich Bullinger zuͦ Zürich.</s>
				</p>
